{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be sophisticated and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureSphere Cybersecurity</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #e50914; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #f5f5f5; /* Off-white */\n            --dark-text: #333333;\n            --light-text: #ffffff;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            background-color: rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.8); /* Slightly transparent red */\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: var(--light-text);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n      